  "text": "NOTIFICATION (New Delhi, the 27 th March, 1991) G.S.R.253 - In exercise of the powers conferred by sub-section (2) of section I of the Public Liability Insurance Act, 1991 ( 6 of 1991 ), the Central Government hereby appoints the 1st day of April, 1991 as the date on which the said Act shall come into force. -- 1 of 1 --",
